<%- include('../partials/header') %>

<div class="row g-4">
  <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
    <nav aria-label="breadcrumb" class="mb-3">
      <ol class="breadcrumb"><li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/">Home</a></li><li class="breadcrumb-item active">Advertise With Us</li></ol>
    </nav>

    <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm p-4 p-md-5">
      <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span style="background:var(--gradient);width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">
          <i class="bi bi-bullseye text-white fs-5"></i>
        </span>
        <div>
          <h1 class="h3 fw-bold mb-0">Advertise With Us</h1>
          <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Reach a highly engaged news audience</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-content">
        <p class="lead">ApolloNews attracts a growing audience of news-conscious, digitally engaged readers across India and globally. Advertising with us puts your brand in front of an audience that is actively seeking information.</p>

        <h4 class="fw-bold mt-4">Why Advertise on ApolloNews?</h4>
        <div class="row g-3 my-2">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="border rounded p-3 h-100">
              <i class="bi bi-people-fill fs-4 mb-2" style="color:var(--primary);"></i>
              <h6 class="fw-bold">Engaged Readership</h6>
              <p class="small text-muted mb-0">Our readers spend significant time on-site reading in-depth articles across technology, business, health, and more.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="border rounded p-3 h-100">
              <i class="bi bi-clock-history fs-4 mb-2" style="color:var(--primary);"></i>
              <h6 class="fw-bold">Constantly Fresh Content</h6>
              <p class="small text-muted mb-0">With news refreshed every 10 minutes, readers return multiple times a day — giving your ads repeated visibility.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="border rounded p-3 h-100">
              <i class="bi bi-geo-alt-fill fs-4 mb-2" style="color:var(--primary);"></i>
              <h6 class="fw-bold">India-Focused Traffic</h6>
              <p class="small text-muted mb-0">Strong concentration of Indian readers across Tier 1 and Tier 2 cities — ideal for brands targeting the Indian market.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="border rounded p-3 h-100">
              <i class="bi bi-phone-fill fs-4 mb-2" style="color:var(--primary);"></i>
              <h6 class="fw-bold">Mobile-First Design</h6>
              <p class="small text-muted mb-0">Our fully responsive Site ensures premium ad visibility on mobile devices, where most Indian internet users browse.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h4 class="fw-bold mt-4">Advertising Options</h4>
        <div class="table-responsive">
          <table class="table table-bordered mt-3">
            <thead class="table-dark">
              <tr><th>Format</th><th>Placement</th><th>Dimensions</th></tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>Leaderboard Banner</td><td>Top of page, Homepage &amp; all inner pages</td><td>728×90px / responsive</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Rectangle</td><td>Sidebar, Article pages</td><td>300×250px</td></tr>
              <tr><td>In-Feed Ad</td><td>Between article listings</td><td>Native / responsive</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Sponsored Content</td><td>Clearly labelled blog post</td><td>Full article format</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Newsletter Sponsorship</td><td>Coming soon — email digest</td><td>Custom</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h4 class="fw-bold mt-4">Our Advertising Policy</h4>
        <p>All advertisements on ApolloNews must comply with our advertising standards:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Ads must not be misleading, deceptive, or make unverified health or financial claims</li>
          <li>No advertising for illegal products, services, or activities</li>
          <li>Sponsored content is clearly labelled as "Sponsored" or "Advertisement"</li>
          <li>Advertising relationships do not influence editorial decisions</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We reserve the right to decline or remove any advertisement that does not comply with our standards or is inappropriate for our audience.</p>

        <div class="alert alert-primary mt-4">
          <h5 class="fw-bold"><i class="bi bi-envelope-fill me-2"></i>Get in Touch</h5>
          <p class="mb-2">For rates, availability, and custom packages, please contact us with your campaign requirements.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Our Advertising Team</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>
